xxl.core.spatial.histograms.utils

Class MHistograms

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.spatial.histograms.utils.MHistograms

  • public class MHistograms
extends Object
    This class implements spatial histograms for selectivity estimation Assumption: input data is a collection of doublePointRectangles ( DoublePointRectangle ) in unit space!
    See Also:
    Achakeev and B. Seeger A class of R-tree histograms for spatial databases GIS 2012
